{"id": "ChIJZYbYA9O-woARi32xpzX7jDA", "rating": 3.6, "userRatingCount": 196, "displayName": {"text": "2nd STREET Melrose", "languageCode": "ja"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJZYbYA9O-woARi32xpzX7jDA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWUlpsRnVPVXhHVFRjMmNVcFBhMU01TkZjNVVGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I sorta knew what to expect when walking into this shop, but it still surprises me by some of the pieces they had. The employees especially one female and guy with dreads was very helpful in sharing with me information that I was curious about on brands. It's definitely overly crowded by so many different people that I can understand why security is needed, so I'd say if you're browsing then you can't go wrong. But to make a purchase definitely try them on, feel it on, and walk around to see if it's really something you'd want.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I sorta knew what to expect when walking into this shop, but it still surprises me by some of the pieces they had. The employees especially one female and guy with dreads was very helpful in sharing with me information that I was curious about on brands. It's definitely overly crowded by so many different people that I can understand why security is needed, so I'd say if you're browsing then you can't go wrong. But to make a purchase definitely try them on, feel it on, and walk around to see if it's really something you'd want.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ethan Yuen", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105383201739400293073/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWMTfYDe5X5CBUfwvc1Bq02ULQ4_Gs92M0tfhIFpq-nQlvteyY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-10T08:31:44.187807850Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWUlpsRnVPVXhHVFRjMmNVcFBhMU01TkZjNVVGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWUlpsRnVPVXhHVFRjMmNVcFBhMU01TkZjNVVGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bed303d88665:0x308cfb35a7b17d8b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJZYbYA9O-woARi32xpzX7jDA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoeGFHZFVaVEpVTTI5SVYyTmplR3Q2U2t0T2VGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "The two guys helping me were very nice and straight forward. I forgot my slip but I described my bag and they remembered which one it was and didn’t make a big deal out of it which was appreciated. Took 2 hours on a Saturday for just one bag of clothes. Come prepared to hang in the area for a while! Simple designer clothes won’t do well here, only sell/ bring interesting or unique items.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The two guys helping me were very nice and straight forward. I forgot my slip but I described my bag and they remembered which one it was and didn’t make a big deal out of it which was appreciated. Took 2 hours on a Saturday for just one bag of clothes. Come prepared to hang in the area for a while! Simple designer clothes won’t do well here, only sell/ bring interesting or unique items.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "AN", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113755321957944268529/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUblSTSP1tHZPY4ymjjBqJ_PotIGBY0j-d2LKV5TrqAObvXleHg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-12T01:42:26.611505934Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoeGFHZFVaVEpVTTI5SVYyTmplR3Q2U2t0T2VGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoeGFHZFVaVEpVTTI5SVYyTmplR3Q2U2t0T2VGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bed303d88665:0x308cfb35a7b17d8b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJZYbYA9O-woARi32xpzX7jDA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOdFRtRkljalJSTkV0aFdraHFXa1ZoTkY5aWRYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Took some clothes in to sell on a Friday around 3:00 PM. The girl told me it would be around two hours until they could make me an offer and I said that was fine. She told me they would call me when it was ready. I received no call at 5 when she said they would. I didn’t receive a call until 7:30 (30 min before close) saying that I need to come pick my clothes up before 8 or they’ll donate them. They obviously wait until the last second so that you can’t make it to the store in time and they can keep your clothes to profit off of without having to pay you.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Took some clothes in to sell on a Friday around 3:00 PM. The girl told me it would be around two hours until they could make me an offer and I said that was fine. She told me they would call me when it was ready. I received no call at 5 when she said they would. I didn’t receive a call until 7:30 (30 min before close) saying that I need to come pick my clothes up before 8 or they’ll donate them. They obviously wait until the last second so that you can’t make it to the store in time and they can keep your clothes to profit off of without having to pay you.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Eden Al Qahtani", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107928486329910397161/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoIvupF0lPBfLxhQ5MBbpJcLxTHvDDkc9Yrluwd0CdN66Jei8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-12T17:19:52.441696760Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOdFRtRkljalJSTkV0aFdraHFXa1ZoTkY5aWRYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOdFRtRkljalJSTkV0aFdraHFXa1ZoTkY5aWRYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bed303d88665:0x308cfb35a7b17d8b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJZYbYA9O-woARi32xpzX7jDA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RemEyMWlWMEZOVjJaUWIxRjRlbXRETTBwdE9GRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My son wanted to go here to pick up a few second hand pieces... When I walked in the atmosphere is very young, nice music. There is a lot of nice clothing and shoes and accessories. The prices are reasonable for the specific pieces, depending on your taste.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My son wanted to go here to pick up a few second hand pieces... When I walked in the atmosphere is very young, nice music. There is a lot of nice clothing and shoes and accessories. The prices are reasonable for the specific pieces, depending on your taste.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Carissa Dean", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101103969840205759458/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLnHuE6R413budzMVb_dhQ_IFULMgtbA-XsNNW8TNomNoQFW6s=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-31T21:14:10.362164813Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RemEyMWlWMEZOVjJaUWIxRjRlbXRETTBwdE9GRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RemEyMWlWMEZOVjJaUWIxRjRlbXRETTBwdE9GRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bed303d88665:0x308cfb35a7b17d8b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJZYbYA9O-woARi32xpzX7jDA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jelMyTnNaRTV2ZEZGdlpWbHhjMjVZTms1MlVVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Prices are ok. Great selection. Security is nice. Many rude staff members. Customers seem to be an inconvenience. Maybe they need a reminder that customers are who pay their checks and keep the doors open. Be happy customers are there to spend money.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Prices are ok. Great selection. Security is nice. Many rude staff members. Customers seem to be an inconvenience. Maybe they need a reminder that customers are who pay their checks and keep the doors open. Be happy customers are there to spend money.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anthony Williams", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114724927764802550381/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHG56Bs9FnKJDntBcSASlwhAEw8pUreKRbF02tvzKp6GvUm_IvJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-17T23:48:12.959278347Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jelMyTnNaRTV2ZEZGdlpWbHhjMjVZTms1MlVVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jelMyTnNaRTV2ZEZGdlpWbHhjMjVZTms1MlVVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bed303d88665:0x308cfb35a7b17d8b"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJZYbYA9O-woARi32xpzX7jDA/photos/AWCwydj5-Ajw4w-T7I7PYopcwkHsU1nBuarzh0vKyzz3mOrjPi74plbbs_klVOvcbkb8WaZh3vinihISI5QpCXl8szQD5XuUaJD__wqDiWaxuYVI1yDiX9zdoUAx1mcp1gkjwif3U7O_Emt50RBT6qKhTXZ5h131PoczvEdwn13iGm_AIXWkr5cVhAXG-3I-HOmD_Jt0wyUOaa4l6DSdfsTZDOgraaT0tsrcnAIK5y7FxbSy5h7QBRBNv-aKv2HbmqpKtG115tfbfdYbrslL1SJcPauuSBMmG3B8Rfp4KhaLGbqUorvj9tqkNywnBQ4v4cPaSv9eVETn8eyDULksnRXc_8mPS42xFHN6QxN6JioN95JAJ05OeGL7H6tbyW-2XKW0afWBVj_z8bA6CQoC544hAaaZ5bBtENhPLC_nv9PUrlEh1Q", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 3200, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "2nd STREET Melrose", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/101807194111094489491", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfR2kzpfHkcZgoKDF1HHNjda5Gnzglj_dww5nFBYXgE8rSndI=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgIC6tJrGVw&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIHM0ogKEICAgIC6tJrGVw!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x80c2bed303d88665:0x308cfb35a